settings.title: Shipping & Delivery
How long will my order take to reach me?
settings.text:
Standard Shipping

Cover-Up customers live all across the globe, so we can ship to anywhere with a letterbox.

We usually dispatch orders within 1-2 working days. Shipping times vary based on selected service and destination. Regular post ranges from 3 to 28 working days depending on the shipping address.

For a shipping estimate to your country, please see our Shipping page.
